        "content": "<p>#include &lt;iostream&gt;<br />\r\nusing namespace std ;<br />\r\nvoid swap( int *a, int *b ) {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;int temp = *a ;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;*a = *b ;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;*b = temp ;<br />\r\n}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>int main()<br />\r\n{<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;int a = 2 ;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;int b = 3 ;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;cout &lt;&lt; &quot;a = &quot; &lt;&lt; a &lt;&lt; &quot; &nbsp;b = &quot; &lt;&lt; b &lt;&lt; endl ;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;swap( &amp;a, &amp;b ) ; // 傳入a,b的記憶體位址<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;cout &lt;&lt; &quot;a = &quot; &lt;&lt; a &lt;&lt; &quot; &nbsp;b = &quot; &lt;&lt; b &lt;&lt; endl ;<br />\r\n}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>輸出</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/user/1/0/10927230/images/image2\" style=\"height:59px; width:194px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>也叫call by pointer，把a和b記憶體位址傳入function後，並作為&quot;指向記憶體位址的指標&quot; 來使用</p>",
